summary:
EightBit Me - A collection of 8,888 NFT’s that are generated by countless 8-bit themed traits. Within the collection, there are rare outfits, items, and more surprises.

 Roadmap: Season 1 - Information about the NFT Mint, Perks, Gallery, Shop, EightBit + Turf, Builder, and Loot.

 Our Origin Story - Information about the launch of the original 8-bit avatar creator in 2010 and the goal of the EightBit project.
